	<transcript sound="sound1"><![CDATA[Welcome to module 3.<br /><br />In this module we will find out more about food poisoning and its control.<br /><br />We will learn what causes food poisoning, the signs and symptoms of a person suffering from food poisoning and how to prevent it.]]></transcript>
	
	<transcript sound="sound2"><![CDATA[Let's first understand the meaning of a few terms relating to food poisoning.<br /><br />Click a term on the left and then match it to its meaning by clicking on a definition, then click ‘Check Answer’ to see if you are right.]]></transcript>
	
